'''Apolinary Kowalski''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[World Mixed Pairs Championship]] (1) 1994

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** [[Keohane North American Swiss Teams]] (1) 2012 

===Runners-up===

* [[Senior Bowl (bridge)|d'Orsi Senior Bowl]] (2) 2009, 2013 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** [[Keohane North American Swiss Teams]] (1) 2004 

